dct_title_s: Bulkhead and pierhead lines approved by Secretary of War Sept. 13, 1913
dct_description_sm: Map shows the bulkhead and pierhead lines approved by Sec. of War Sept. 13, 1913 along the South, East and West sides of Newark Bay; map shows Bergen Pt. Light, Centerville, Pamrano Light, Junction Light; attached to map is a list of companies and payment amounts
